    </div>
    
    <div class="sidebar-section">
      <h3>Key Takeaways</h3>
      <ul class="key-points">
        <li>Stress responses are automatic and protective</li>
        <li>Fight, flight, freeze, and fawn are all survival strategies</li>
        <li>Chronic stress changes how your nervous system works</li>
        <li>Understanding is not excusing</li>
        <li>Recovery is possible with support</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </aside>
</ArticleLayout>

